==Min Nan==
===Pronunciation===
*{{IPA|[ tui˥˧put˥˥kʰi˥˧ ]}}

===Verb===
{{nan-verb|t|poj=tùi-put-khí|pojt=tui3put4khi2|tra=對不起|sim=对不起|rs=寸11}}

# to cause someone embarassment; to screw someone over; to do something to a person that would demand an apology later on

===Usage notes===
*'''tùi-put-khí''' is not often used as an interjection meaning ''I'm sorry'' in Min Nan.  Use [[歹勢]] ([[phái-sè]]) or [[失禮]] ([[sit-lé]]) instead.

